sentence: Other key speakers included Mrs F.T. Swanwick, suffragist and editor of the NUWSS paper the Common Cause: Kathleen Courtney, secretary of the North of England Society for Women's Suffrage; Lisbeth Simms of the Women's Labour League; Margaret Robertson BA Manchester Society / NUWSS organiser: and a Manchester councillor, Margaret Ashton, founder member of the Women's Trade Union League and chairperson of the NUWSS.
